OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,FWaiting lists in Wales still have a
OL,7,F"very long way to go", despite seeing
OL,8,Fa "very small fall" for the third
OL,9,Fconsecutive month, a top doctor has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FNew data published today (21 March)
OL,13,Fshows that the waiting list for
OL,14,Freferral to treatment in Wales has
OL,15,Fseen another small decrease, with the
OL,16,Ffigure for January 2024 sitting at
OL,17,Fjust over 755,400, down from over
OL,18,F756,300 in December 2023.
