OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,FResponding to the figures, Professor
OL,7,FJon Barry, Director in Wales at the
OL,8,FRoyal College of Surgeons of England,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Waiting lists have seen a very
OL,10,Fsmall fall for the third consecutive
OL,11,Fmonth. However, there's a very long
OL,12,Fway to go to get lists back to an
OL,13,Facceptable level ` especially at the
OL,14,Fcurrent rate.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
