OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,F"We are particularly concerned about
OL,7,Fpatients waiting more than one and
OL,8,Feven two years for treatment. They
OL,9,Fwill be suffering huge disruption to
OL,10,Ftheir lives and there is a risk that
OL,11,Ftheir condition will deteriorate while
OL,12,Fthey wait.
OL,14,F"The government in Wales needs to up
OL,15,Fthe pace of investment in both staff,
OL,16,Fand in surgical hubs, to see waiting
OL,17,Flists improve at the rate that is
OL,18,Fneeded."
