OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,FThe patient pathway data released by
OL,7,FStats Wales covers the time a patient
OL,8,Fwaits from their referral to hospital
OL,9,Ffor treatment.
OL,11,FThe data includes time spent waiting
OL,12,Ffor any hospital appointments, tests,
OL,13,Fsurgery, scans, or other procedures.
OL,15,FIt shows that there were just over
OL,16,F23,400 pathways waiting more than two
OL,17,Fyears. There were also around 138,000
OL,18,Fwaiting more than one year in January
OL,19,F2024.
