OL,6,FThe longest waits are for trauma and
OL,7,Forthopaedic treatment, general
OL,8,Fsurgery, Ear, Nose and Throat (ENT),
OL,9,Fand urology.
OL,11,FHowever, the proportion waiting less
OL,12,Fthan 26 weeks decreased and the number
OL,13,Fwaiting longer than 36 weeks increased.
OL,15,FThe Health Minister Eluned Morgan told
OL,16,FITV Wales in December last year that
OL,17,Fshe would after a new First Minister
OL,18,Fof Wales is appointed.
OL,20,FMs Morgan described her job as "very,
OL,21,Fvery tough".
