OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,F"Obviously I know how the system works
OL,7,Fnow, I know where the problems are and
OL,8,FI've got an idea on how to fix them,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"But it's not a job you can do for
OL,12,Fvery long, I don't think, with the
OL,13,Fpressure that you're under."
OL,15,FThe data also showed that average
OL,16,Fresponse times to immediately life-
OL,17,Fthreatening (red) calls were 10
OL,18,Fseconds faster when compared to the
OL,19,Fprevious month, with 80% receiving a
OL,20,Fresponse in 15 minutes.
