OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said
OL,7,Fthis is a "remarkable achievement by
OL,8,Four hard-working NHS staff considering
OL,9,Fit included a period of industrial
OL,10,Faction as well as the usual pressures
OL,11,Fon the system seen in January.
OL,13,F"The proportion of red calls was the
OL,14,Fjoint third highest on record. We
OL,15,Fexpect to see health boards improve
OL,16,Fambulance patient handover performance
OL,17,Fas a priority to support more timely
OL,18,Fambulance responses.
