OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,F"The average time patients waited for
OL,7,Ftriage and then to be assessed by a
OL,8,Fclinician in emergency departments was
OL,9,F18 and 58 minutes respectively.
OL,11,F"We have challenged health boards to
OL,12,Fmake improvements on these and other
OL,13,Fkey measures as part of our new
OL,14,FQuality Statement for Care in
OL,15,FEmergency Departments, published last
OL,16,Fweek."
OL,18,FThey added: "It is disappointing to
OL,19,Fsee one-year waits for a first
OL,20,Foutpatient appointment increase again
OL,21,Fhowever.
