OL,3,CWaiting lists in Wales have 'long way
OL,4,Cto go' to return to 'acceptable level'
OL,6,F"February also saw an increase in the
OL,7,Ftotal number of pathways of care
OL,8,Fdischarge delays compared to the
OL,9,Fprevious month, which reflects the
OL,10,Fdifficulties of the impacts of winter
OL,11,Fpressures on both our health and
OL,12,Fsocial care sectors. Although the
OL,13,Ftotal for Wales has increased we have
OL,14,Falso seen some encouraging
OL,15,Fimprovements within some regions in
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,F"There remains much more to do, but we
OL,19,Fare encouraged by the direction in
OL,20,Fwhich the major statistics are
OL,21,Ftrending."
