OL,6,FNesta Lloyd-Jones, assistant director
OL,7,Fof the Welsh NHS Confederation, said:
OL,8,F"There are some indications of
OL,9,Fprogress in planned care, with the
OL,10,Foverall number of patient pathways
OL,11,Fcoming down slightly in January, and
OL,12,Fthose waiting more than two years
OL,13,Fcontinues to fall month on month,
OL,14,Fshowing the concerted effort by health
OL,15,Fboards to target the longest waiters.
