OL,6,FShe continued: "It's vital Wales' new
OL,7,FFirst Minister and the Minister for
OL,8,FHealth and Social Services engage with
OL,9,Fhealth trade unions to prevent further
OL,10,Findustrial action in the NHS.
OL,11,FIndustrial action is and will continue
OL,12,Fto have a huge impact on service
OL,13,Fdelivery, undoing much of the good
OL,14,Fwork that has been done to recover
OL,15,Fperformance following the pandemic.
