OL,6,F"Resolving trade union disputes and
OL,7,Finvesting in social care, workforce,
OL,8,Fcapital and digital are the NHS's only
OL,9,Fchance to free up patient flow in
OL,10,Fhospitals and have the capacity to
OL,11,Freduce both urgent & emergency care
OL,12,Fand planned care waiting times,
OL,13,Fultimately improving outcomes for
OL,14,Fpatients. In the longer term,
OL,15,Faddressing inequalities and the wider
OL,16,Fdeterminants of health will be our
OL,17,Fonly hope of sustainable health and
OL,18,Fcare services and supporting a
OL,19,Fhealthier population."
